# Persona Studio — testing rules

- Run tests with `npm run test` (Vitest). Tests live in `tests/persona-studio/`.
- Cover: schema validation, evidence/quote/confidence vocabulary, confidence &
  coverage math, seed integrity, chat structured output, anti-stereotype audit
  output. Playwright journeys land in Phase 4.
- **Never delete or skip a failing test to make a build pass.** Fix the cause.
- Seed data must always validate against the schemas (`seed-integrity.test.ts`).
- Before claiming done: `npm run lint`, `npx tsc --noEmit`, `npm run test` and
  `npm run build` must all pass.
